Oklahoma-Bred money to b e divided 60% to the winner, 20% to second, 11% to third, 6% to fourth, and 3% to fifth. Weights: Three-Year-Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 124 lbs. Non-winners of $30,000 twice in 2022-23 allowed 3 lbs.; of $30,000 once in 2022-23, 6 lbs. Starters to be named th rough the entry box by usual time of entry.
